        "checksum": "e4a4d83226d9e6f672e55c385dfe6d7435229a1f54a0192a21f4c3a270f9656c_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg34cF7Ioxz_text": "<u>Frequently asked questions</u>",
        "gg9SzSdtOLt_text": "<p>My doctor kept wanting to put me on antidepressants but I tried this first and thank god I did. Feel like myself again without all the weird side effects</p>",
        "gg9d3DIlKM9_text": "<p>If you're experiencing subtle decline but function still works most of the time, you're early. The test strips will show if your nitric oxide levels are low—that's your objective measure. Early intervention works best when decline is noticed but not yet significant.</p>",
        "ggF1V3gbwGf_text": "<p><strong>Peter S. 48</strong></p>",
        "ggG0BS0k_Cp_text": "<p><i>I did the test strip and my NO level was very low. Then I took 2 caps of Nitric Oxide Foundation that came n the sample pack, waited 90 minutes. After 90 minutes I retested and my NO level was on the high end. I did not expect that. Genius way of showing the effectiveness of the supplement. I am very impressed.</i></p>",
        "ggGzD05QpRq_text": "<p>Berkeley Life supports foundational blood flow health. Some men find their overall vascular health improves significantly with consistent use, which they discuss with their doctors during regular checkups. Our focus is on providing root-cause support that complements your existing protocol, not replacing other treatments.</p>",
        "ggJ_fwPKbcz_text": "<p><i>Since day 1, I noticed a significance right away. I’ve tried many N O supplements by far this ranks 1, for me its purity and quality, but most of all it does what it says, that’s nice 😊 to have a standard 963 much needed in this world 🌎 thank you 🙏</i><br>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggNQUd1xCSO_text": "<strong>What Men Are Saying</strong>",
        "ggWVfpqvg9H_text": "<p><strong>Jovani Q. 40</strong></p>",
        "ggXqsiHg2xM_text": "<p>Most men notice improved morning readiness within 2 weeks (sign of better natural blood flow), more sustained energy throughout the day, faster recovery from exercise, and overall sense of vitality. Test strips show objective improvement in nitric oxide levels. You're supporting total cardiovascular health, not just one symptom.</p>",
        "ggZwfiFFxMk_text": "<p><strong>Rebecca S., 51</strong></p>",
        "gg_D_QMySBg_text": "<p><i>Since I have been taking Berkeley lights nitric acid foundation I have seen my energy levels increase, I also do a lot of cardio running and cycling and have seen benefits as well. Highly recommend.</i></p>",
        "gg_bVFv9waw_text": "<p><strong>Mateo S. 44</strong></p>",
        "ggcLOFavrpo_text": "<p><strong>David K., 56</strong></p>",
        "ggd9CVWV8Oo_text": "<p>Yes. Berkeley Life is safe to use alongside prescription ED medications. They work through different mechanisms—Berkeley Life supports nitric oxide production (foundational), while medications block PDE5 enzymes (symptom management). Many men value having both approaches working together. Always discuss additions to your protocol with your healthcare provider.</p>",
        "gghzkoHyojV_text": "<strong>Where To Go From Here</strong>",
        "ggiOTE1v3r2_text": "<p>You'd need to consume 7 ounces of beetroot daily to match the concentrated nitrate dose in Berkeley Life's formula. Most people can't sustain that dietary change consistently. Supplementation ensures you get therapeutic levels daily.</p>",
        "gglxyFhpObR_childItem_0": "<p><strong>How do I know if I'm catching this early enough?</strong></p>",
        "gglxyFhpObR_childItem_1": "<p><strong>Can I just eat more beets instead of taking a supplement?</strong></p>",
        "gglxyFhpObR_childItem_2": "<p><strong>How is this different from what my medication does?</strong></p>",
        "gglxyFhpObR_childItem_3": "<p><strong>What improvements should I expect?</strong></p>",
        "ggmFQXT5WBV_text": "<p>Medications force temporary blood vessel dilation by blocking PDE5 enzymes. Berkeley Life supports your body's natural nitric oxide production, which affects blood flow continuously, not just temporarily. It's the difference between forcing a response and supporting the natural mechanism.</p>",
        "ggq3WxWMIcn_text": "<p><i>I've been using this N.O project since 2022, for me it took awhile for it start kicking in for me because I had some underline issues I had to get in control, one was my weight, high blood pressure, diabetes and mildly sexual performance issues. To this product testimony, I worked on myself dropping 40lbs off my weight, that was the big issue and changing my eating habits. That's when this product kicked into full gear for me , my blood pressure start stabilizing, I had good circulation going through my veins, I dropped my A1C to 6.2 from 7.1 My sexual performance got stronger. This product works if you take care of the underline things, I did not had to do a lot to get here. but have this N.O product alone with the test strips to monitor, helped my out tremendously!!! Thank Berkley's for a great product</i></p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_0": "<p>What's the correct dosage and how should I take it?</p>",
        "ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_1": "<p><strong>Can I take this with my current prescription medication?</strong></p>",
        "ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_2": "<p><strong>Will this replace my need for medication?</strong></p>",
        "ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_3": "<p>How long until I see results?</p>",
        "ggufosgqD8__text": "<p>Results vary, some notice a difference right away, while others see benefits after about a month. Consistency is key, and test strips can validate improvements quickly.</p>",
        "ggvTXmAqSlk_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);color:rgb(11,11,11);font-size:16px;\">Take two capsules daily with water, preferably after a meal.</span></p>",
        "ggwqA6Cy44q_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Two capsules daily. 24-hour support means one morning dose covers you continuously. Plant-based formula—beetroot-derived nitrates plus vitamin C and magnesium for optimal conversion and vascular support.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">This integrates seamlessly with your existing stack. No conflicts, no timing issues. It enhances everything else you're taking by ensuring nutrients actually get delivered to tissues efficiently. Think of it as optimizing the logistics system—your supplements are the cargo, blood flow is the delivery mechanism.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The investment is $42.49 per month with subscription. Comparable to quality pre-workout, less than most protein powder, fraction of what high-performers typically spend monthly on optimization. ROI is significant, one supplement that makes everything else work better.</span></p>"
